'''Coiling tack''' were special accountrements that [[Swokes Swokes/Legends|Swokes Swokes]] would outfit their [[Schinga]] mounts with. A set of coiling tack included a gold-inlaid saddle, a bit, bridle and reins, and a long-handled Schinga [[Electropole/Legends|Electropole]].

